HINT: 1) Ensure a BM25 index exists on this JSON column
2) Configure jsonb_values_paths: ALTER INDEX idx SET (jsonb_values_paths = '{...}')
3) Use explicit cast syntax: column::pdb.jsonb_values
DROP INDEX IF EXISTS jsonb_values_no_field_idx;
